OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 18 MAY
OL,4,G2200FGluck: Who Did She Think He Was?
OL,5,     GThe story of Gluck - Britain's
OL,6,     Gcross-dressing high society
OL,7,     Gpainter of the 1930s - who staged
OL,8,     G'one-man shows', had
OL,9,     Grelationships with women and
OL,10,     Gsomehow got away with it.
OL,11,G2300FAn Art Lovers' Guide
OL,12,     GJanina and Alastair discover Baku
OL,13,     Gin Azerbaijan through its art and
OL,14,     Garchitecture.
OL,15,G0000FArt That Made Us
OL,16,     GThe world wars force artists to
OL,17,     Ggrapple with destruction and
OL,18,     Gsavagery, challenging conventions
OL,19,     Gand the old imperial order, while
OL,20,     Gthose fleeing war bring new ideas
OL,21,     Gto Britain.
